     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       str vrythng n txt fls
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Whn t cms t tchnlgy, I strngly blv tht smplr s bttr.
      </p>
      <p>
       W tnd t tk dvntg f r ncrsngly pwrfl cmptng pwr by lwys ncrsng th cmplxty f r tsks nd dt — n lngr s vrythng txt-bsd (s th wb sd t b, wy bck whn), bt nw vrythng s grphcl nd ncrsngly ss vd.
      </p>
      <p>
       Th rslt s  rchr vsl prsnttn, whch s wndrfl, bt t th sm tm pgs r slwr t ld, pplctns bcm bltd nd frz p, nd nfrmtn tht cld b prsntd smply nd qckly s nw prsntd v vd, mkng s wt mnts jst t gt n r tw ky pcs f nfrmtn.
      </p>
      <p>
       Cmplxty s bltd, slw, brdnsm. Wrs yt, r dt s ftn td p n prprtry frmts, n dtbss tht cn gt crrpt, n frmts tht dn’t spk t thr prgrms.
      </p>
      <p>
       Smplcty s fst, ln, lght. Dt n smpl frmts — sch s txt — s mbl, cn b prtd t ny prgrm, s nt lckd nt  prprtry prgrm r dtbs.
      </p>
      <p>
       I’m mvng mr nd mr twrd txt fls, ftr hvng bn  fn f mr cmplx frmts nd prgrms fr  fw yrs.
       <br/>
       <span id="more-347">
       </span>
       <br/>
       I lv prgrms lk
       <a href="http://www.evernote.com/">
        Evrnt
       </a>
       ,
       <a href="http://shawnblanc.net/2009/09/yojimbo-and-anything-buckets/">
        Yjmb
       </a>
       , vn th smpl
       <a href="http://notational.net/">
        Nttnl Vlcty
       </a>
       — bt th trth s, txt fls r jst s gd. And thy’r fstr nd smplr.
      </p>
      <p>
       I cn ld my fvrt txt dtr (
       <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/TextEdit">
        TxtEdt
       </a>
       , spr smpl) nd b typng n tw scnds. It tks  fw xtr scnds t ld  bggr prgrm sch s Evrnt r Yjmb, nd ch f ths tks p wy mr systm mmry nd slws thngs dwn. Evn th lghtwght Nttnl Vlcty,  grt prgrm, strs nf n  dtbs tht cn b crrptd, n  frmt tht cn’t b prtd lswhr.
      </p>
      <p>
       Whl I lv grphcl prgrms, thy r jst vrkll fr my nds. Yr nds my b mr cmplx, mr dmndng, bt mn rn’t.
      </p>
      <p>
       I wrt psts, rtcls, bks n TxtEdt (r
       <a href="http://www.hogbaysoftware.com/products/writeroom">
        WrtRm
       </a>
       , whn I fl t mny dstrctns), thn pst thm whrvr thy’r ndd.
      </p>
      <p>
       I kp nts, td lsts (whn I nd thm), thr nf I nd svd, n  txt fl r thr. Thy cn b pppd pn n hlf  scnd, nd wth  qck “Fnd” cmmnd, I cn fnd ny nf.
      </p>
      <p>
       Agn, my nds r prpsly smpl. And txt fls r prpsly mnmlst, lghtwght, fst, ln, nd thsly btfl.
       <br/>
       —
